text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to see page likes on facebook?
text.Response A: Sure, I can tell you.  I don’t have a facebook account, but I’ve read about it online.  You should click on the “like” button to like a page.  Then, if you go to the page, you should see the number of likes next to the “like” button.
text.Response B: To see your page likes on Facebook, go to your Facebook page and click on the 'Likes' button in the left-hand menu. From there, you can see the total number of likes your page has, as well as a breakdown of where those likes are coming from. You can also access a more detailed view by clicking on 'See All' under the 'Likes' button.

Prompt

Can you tell me how to see page likes on facebook?

Response A

Sure, I can tell you. I don’t have a facebook account, but I’ve read about it online. You should click on the “like” button to like a page. Then, if you go to the page, you should see the number of likes next to the “like” button.

Response B

To see your page likes on Facebook, go to your Facebook page and click on the 'Likes' button in the left-hand menu. From there, you can see the total number of likes your page has, as well as a breakdown of where those likes are coming from. You can also access a more detailed view by clicking on 'See All' under the 'Likes' button.
